release_notes:
This is a macOS only hot fix from the 2024.3.407.0 release.

## Notable updates
- Fixed an issue by correcting the WARP client setting of macOS firewall rules. This relates to TunnelVision (CVE-2024-3661).

## Known issues
 - No known issues.

For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
